data.text:
The Proximity Playlist – Levi Ouimet

This week’s episode of The Proximity Playlist with Gino D, focuses on Levi Ouimet, a talented musician now based in Chattanooga. Originally from Lynchburg, Virginia, Levi has a rich history of musical exploration and growth.

Levi’s musical journey began in his childhood with the piano, quickly transitioning to the guitar, which has been his steadfast companion ever since. His early experiences playing in church bands laid the groundwork for a diverse career that took him to Nashville, where he immersed himself in various genres and collaborated with a range of local artists.

Rediscovering his passion for music, Levi focused on his original compositions, leading to the recording of his EP in Nashville. In this episode, you’ll hear about Levi’s experiences, the evolution of his sound, and his exciting plans for the future. Sit back and enjoy as we bring you the story and music of Levi Ouimet on ‘The Proximity Playlist.’
